v 3
d projectinit - Professional Research Project Initializer
d
d projectinit creates professional, reproducible research project structures
d following international best practices from J-PAL (MIT), DIME (World Bank),
d the AEA Data Editor, and NBER.
d
d The command generates a complete project infrastructure including:
d - Standardized folder structure (01_Data, 02_Scripts, 03_Outputs, etc.)
d - Master execution script (run.do) with environment isolation
d - Setup and configuration scripts (00_setup.do)
d - Elite .gitignore for version control
d - AEA-compliant README.md with replication instructions
d - Optional LaTeX environment (PUC thesis or standard article)
d - Optional GitHub repository initialization
d - Optional AEA replication package (06_Replication/)
d
d The project structure ensures reproducibility, portability, isolation,
d comprehensive documentation, version control readiness, and compliance
d with AEA, J-PAL, DIME, and NBER standards.
d
d KW: project management
d KW: reproducible research
d KW: workflow
d KW: directory structure
d KW: version control
d
d Requires: Stata version 14.0
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260122
d License: MIT
d
d Author: Maykol Medrano
d Support: email mmedrano2@uc.cl
d
f projectinit.ado
f projectinit.sthlp
